    {
      "role": "body",
      "left_in": 7.575215441819773,
      "top_in": 2.993536745406824,
      "width_in": 5.2493438320209975,
      "height_in": 2.3673392388451444,
      "text": "1. MIPROv2 proposes instructions and searches combinations - but it only sees final scores. It has no access to why a prompt failed at each step of the trace.2. GEPA reads the full execution trace (reasoning, tool calls, outputs) and reflects in natural language to diagnose the problem. It then proposes a targeted prompt fix based on that diagnosis.",
